Download/Tutorial






Feel free to use and modify my codes as long as proper credit is given. Please don’t redistribute them without permission.



nib.scss
ink.scss
To use this theme in Quarto, download the files above and add the following configuration to _quarto.yml:
format:
  html:
    theme:
      light: 
        - morph
        - nib.scss
      dark: 
        - morph
        - ink.scss
To customize color schemes, paste 6-digit HEX codes in corresponding places:
/* Color Palette */
$body-bg: #f4f4f4;
$body-color: #222222;
$link-color: #635d5d;
$link-hover-color: #9f3838;
$code-color: #222222;
$code-bg: #e7e7e7;
$code-block-bg: $code-bg;

